# Title: Steganography Hide Files with Steghide
# Author: Pawel Mazur
# Date: 2021-09-11
# Level: low
# Description: Detects embedding of files with usage of steghide binary, the adversaries may use this technique to prevent the detection of hidden information.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/execve/lnx_auditd_steghide_embed_steganography.yml

a0="steghide" a1="embed" a2 IN ("-cf", "-ef") a4 IN ("-cf", "-ef") type="EXECVE"